BUSINESS REQUIREMENT DOCUMENT (BRD)

1️⃣ Executive Summary
The Resume & Job Application Auto-Bot is a Python-based automation system designed to help job seekers:
Analyze job descriptions
Match resume with job requirements
Customize resume summary
Generate tailored cover letters
Apply automatically on selected platforms
Track applications centrally
Target platforms include:
LinkedIn
Naukri.com
Foundit
Indeed

2️⃣ Business Objectives
Objective
Description
Automation
Reduce manual job application effort by 70%
Customization
Improve ATS score through tailored resumes
Efficiency
Apply to multiple jobs within minutes
Tracking
Centralized monitoring of job applications
Monetization
Offer SaaS-based subscription model


3️⃣ Problem Statement
Job seekers:
Manually customize resumes for each job
Spend hours applying individually
Lack tracking mechanism
Do not know resume match percentage
This leads to:
Low response rate
High manual effort
Poor optimization

4️⃣ Scope
✅ In Scope
Resume parsing (.docx)
Job description analysis
Keyword extraction
Match percentage calculation
Resume summary customization
Cover letter generation
Excel-based tracking
Basic web interface
Optional Selenium-based auto apply
❌ Out of Scope (Phase 1)
Full ATS integration
Captcha bypass
Mobile application
Multi-user enterprise dashboard

5️⃣ Stakeholders
Stakeholder
Role
Product Owner
Defines features & roadmap
Developer
Builds Python modules
End User
Job seeker
Admin (Future SaaS)
Manage subscriptions


6️⃣ Business Requirements
BR-01: Resume Analysis
System must read resume and extract text.
BR-02: Job Description Processing
System must accept job description via:
Manual paste
URL scraping (optional)
BR-03: Keyword Matching
System must:
Extract keywords from JD
Compare with resume
Calculate match %
BR-04: Resume Customization
System must rewrite resume summary using AI.
BR-05: Cover Letter Generation
System must generate customized cover letter.
BR-06: Auto Apply
System must apply automatically only when:
Easy Apply button exists
No captcha detected
BR-07: Application Tracking
System must log:
Company
Role
Date
Status
BR-08: Error Handling
System must retry failed API calls up to 3 times.

7️⃣ Success Metrics (KPIs)
KPI
Target
Resume Match Accuracy
≥ 80% keyword relevance
Time Saved
≥ 60% reduction
Application Volume
≥ 20/day
System Stability
99% success rate


8️⃣ Assumptions
User provides clean .docx resume
Job portals do not block automation
OpenAI API is available
9️⃣ Risks & Mitigation
Risk
Mitigation
Automation blocked
Manual fallback mode
API downtime
Retry mechanism
Portal UI changes
Modular Selenium scripts
Legal compliance
Terms review before deployment


